lelele，可以，先给你看我建议改成什么样。还没落代码，这只是我建议你确认的版本。

我建议直接把 [MainViewController.m](/Users/liuyifu/Documents/work/NeoChat/NeoChat/Controller/MainViewController.m#L109) 这一段 `setUpTabBar` 替换成下面这样：

```objc
// 设置全局TabBar外观
- (void)setUpTabBar {
    UITabBar *tabBar = [UITabBar appearance];
    tabBar.translucent = NO;
    tabBar.tintColor = TAB_COLOR;
    tabBar.unselectedItemTintColor = GREY_COLOR;

    if (@available(iOS 13.0, *)) {
        UITabBarAppearance *tabBarAppearance = [[UITabBarAppearance alloc] init];
        [tabBarAppearance configureWithDefaultBackground];
        tabBarAppearance.backgroundColor = WHITE_COLOR;

        UITabBarItemAppearance *itemAppearance = tabBarAppearance.stackedLayoutAppearance;
        itemAppearance.normal.iconColor = GREY_COLOR;
        itemAppearance.normal.titleTextAttributes = @{
            NSForegroundColorAttributeName : GREY_COLOR
        };
        itemAppearance.selected.iconColor = TAB_COLOR;
        itemAppearance.selected.titleTextAttributes = @{
            NSForegroundColorAttributeName : TAB_COLOR
        };

        tabBar.standardAppearance = tabBarAppearance;
        if (@available(iOS 15.0, *)) {
            tabBar.scrollEdgeAppearance = tabBarAppearance;
        }
    } else {
        tabBar.barTintColor = WHITE_COLOR;
        tabBar.shadowImage = [UIImage new];
    }
}
```

这版主要做了 3 件事：

1. 删掉原来盖在 `self.tabBar` 上面的 `floatingView`
2. 不再把 tabBar 强行设成透明背景
3. 明确把未选中态改成灰色、选中态改成绿色

